{"tid":1438784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場咁做係冇用嫁...","createTime":"2019-08-10T01:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T04:20:02.000Z","uid":34663,"like":36,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ecf5b10912a8c93a80dccb14c9922c03cfead0cf","tid":1438784,"uid":34663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:24:34.000Z","msg":"我見而家排開既傳單完全都係新聞向，但係d鬼佬黎到鬼知發生咩事咩？<br />\n<br />\n我認為派傳單既目的：除左令外國遊客知督香港發生乜野事，仲要令佢地知 「面對班狗應該做咩！」<br />\n<br />\n建議文宣組可以出單張關於過住克警出咩旗作出乜野行動，教下遊客應該點做，用咩裝備。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係佢地只會覺得我地係搞事。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"2212b6777f9ad60b4eb3158f09953cf5ca0101e0","tid":1438784,"uid":34663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:24:54.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"453e99a7ccd3bb1bee4aaa028bc13fd6c653da1a","tid":1438784,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:25:28.000Z","msg":"推行動post呀<br />\n<br />\n 【置頂+廣傳】８.１０ 大 埔 逃 生 路 線 圖 （附 廣 場 名）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438647</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d3d1e126387775762c93376f599e9478bc7a8d89","tid":1438784,"uid":34663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2212b6777f9ad60b4eb3158f09953cf5ca0101e0","tid":1438784,"uid":34663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:24:54.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:25:42.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"960751f05ce51445d47db9a122440004793fce90","tid":1438784,"uid":51064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:26:00.000Z","msg":"會去機場既手足！<br />\n可以叫旅客follow ig @freehk_ <br />\n入面有唔同既英文文宣！可以俾佢地搭車睇同之後繼續follow up 香港既新聞！！！！！"},{"pid":"e047c9f41f2c8f71e907c014ca013b1c8942a486","tid":1438784,"uid":34663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3d1e126387775762c93376f599e9478bc7a8d89","tid":1438784,"uid":34663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2212b6777f9ad60b4eb3158f09953cf5ca0101e0","tid":14387